Package se.jguru.nazgul.core.xmlbinding.spi.jaxb.transport.type

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractJaxbAnnotatedTransportType<T>
    Abstract supertype of JAXB-annotated transport types, implying that all subtypes should implement ClassInformationHolder and Serializable.
    JaxbAnnotatedCollection<T extends Collection>
    Transport type representing a Collection (subclass) value.
    JaxbAnnotatedDateTime
    Transport type representing a DateTime value.
    JaxbAnnotatedNull
    Transport type representing a null value.
